title: Wo Long: Fallen Dynasty 8 Minutes of New Gameplay

media:group.media:title: Wo Long: Fallen Dynasty 8 Minutes of New Gameplay
media:group.media:description:
Set in a dark fantasy version of China during its warring Three Kingdoms period of history, Wo Long: Fallen Dynasty is aiming to be bigger in scale than Team Ninja's Nioh games and even more challenging.

While Wo-Long: Fallen Dynasty will launch on Xbox One and Xbox Series X|S as a day-one Game Pass title--it'll also be available on PC, PS5, and PS4 on March 3, 2023.
